These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | iced-tea |
| Food       | asparagus | cabbage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | 7up | hot-chocolate |
| Sport      | skateboarding     | biathlon  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, comedy
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, mexican
1. the dutch is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the dutch is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | comedy  |
| Nationality   | dutch | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
