.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, classical
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, chinese
1. the chinese is on the right of the fan of classical##1
2. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | gospel    |
| Nationality   | indian | chinese |

