.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: french, indian
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, dog
1. the indian is on the left or right of the french##3
2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | french | indian |
| Pet           | dog     | hedgehog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
