The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, entrepreneur
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | camping | magic-tricks |
| Job     | doctor        | entrepreneur |

