.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, roller
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |
| Sport       | swimming  | rugby |
| Transport   | snowmobile | roller |

